{"tid":193272,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"外星人同地球人異常之處！","createTime":"2017-04-09T07:41:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-11T16:10:25.000Z","uid":67026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"27aa3c2ab8aa75a3dbda7ec10c6918f65b637955","tid":193272,"uid":67026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T07:41:04.000Z","msg":"有一日，有個外星人塞咗隻手指落個男人隻耳到 <br />\n塞咗一陣，個男人叫佢咪鬼再塞<br />\n個外星人收咗手，過咗陣又塞返落去<br />\n如此類推，過咗幾次之後，個男人話：你再塞我就閹咗你！<br />\n個外星人唔理，過咗陣又塞返<br />\n個地球人就除咗外星人條褲，發現下面無嘢嘅<br />\n跟住問：「下咁你點同人啪啪啪架?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個外星人笑咗一笑，又擺番隻手指落佢隻耳到"},{"pid":"6235ea99e04e4f323d65407da5fe9ca04b73de4c","tid":193272,"uid":103380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T07:45:04.000Z","msg":"哈"},{"pid":"806fc05a1c05e5582279f2b22ed8e84beee75bc7","tid":193272,"uid":20820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T07:46:39.000Z","msg":"幽默大師"},{"pid":"8c9ca703928436800ced0ae414c4d254c16a9136","tid":193272,"uid":39938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T07:49:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85980c5da9264bf5fe9fe3c40015fef5e6c5aa53","tid":193272,"uid":41270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T07:55:24.000Z","msg":"笑左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abe01bfdac5bf55e982db00bc936b50c32526c58","tid":193272,"uid":3018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T08:53:47.000Z","msg":"哈哈"},{"pid":"729831806d6e8fb4bb72eee94036ea26d7af7ceb","tid":193272,"uid":21664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T08:56:16.000Z","msg":"On9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54189e7be550234ff64448f900c75d92fa75960c","tid":193272,"uid":36026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-